# The build context for docker/cpcd-zigbeed/Dockerfile.multiarch is this whole
# directory (25-RCP-UART-HW/) so the Dockerfile can COPY cpcd/tcp-bus.patch into
# the cpcd build. Keep the context tiny: ignore everything, then re-include only
# the assets the Dockerfile actually needs.
**
!docker/cpcd-zigbeed/**
!cpcd/tcp-bus.patch
